 "remarks": "Experience the best of downtown Stamford living in this bright and spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bath condominium featuring two en-suite bedrooms at 127 Greyrock Place, Unit 612. Designed for today&apos;s lifestyle, the open-concept floor plan offers seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas-perfect for everyday living and entertaining. Expansive windows fill the home with natural light while showcasing beautiful views of the downtown skyline.  Each bedroom features its own private full bath, offering comfort, privacy, and flexibility for guests, roommates, or a home office. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit comfort paired with sought-after building amenities, including a fitness center, club room, 24-hour doorman, and parking.  Ideally located in the heart of downtown Stamford, you&apos;re just moments from award-winning restaurants, shopping, entertainment, parks, Metro-North, and major commuting routes. Enjoy low-maintenance living with exceptional amenities in one of Stamford&apos;s most convenient and vibrant locations.",
